
<div class="row  white-background">
  <div class="col-md-9 col-md-offset-1">

   <h6>Before Starting.</h6>

   <p>To create your bot you must have already created a Facebook Page. Otherwise you will have to</p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/create/"> Create a Facebook Page</a>


   <h6>Let's get started. Watch Our Tutorial.</h6>
   <p>It will take 5 minutes to setup your Bot. We will help you in each step. From integrations to making it intelligent.</p>

   <div>
    <object width="800" height="500">
      <param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/_etwz7NkemE&hl=fr"></param>
      <param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param>
      <embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/_etwz7NkemE&hl=fr" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" target="blank" width="800" height="500"></embed>
